{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0002","text":"愛是這麼片面 矛盾都只不過爲了進展","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","單方面","進展"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["片面","矛盾","進展"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,2,5,3,9,2,0,5,3,9,3,4,5,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["oi3","si6","ze5","mo1","pin2","min6","maau4","teon5","dou1","zi2","bat1","gwo3","liu5","zeon3","zin2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愛是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"片面","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"矛盾","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"只不過","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"爲了","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"進展","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「愛是這麼片面」直接點出愛情的不對等，而「矛盾都只不過爲了進展」則帶有自我安慰或合理化矛盾的意味。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0003","text":"煙花散雲下 繼續有煙","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["短暫","持續"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["煙花","散","繼續"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,9,0,2,4,2,5,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin1","faa1","saan2","wan4","haa6","gai3","zuk6","jau5","jin1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"煙花","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"散雲下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"繼續","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有煙","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「煙花散雲下」比喻美好事物的短暫消逝，但「繼續有煙」則暗示了某種延續或殘留。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0004","text":"開心可以過一天","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["當下","快樂"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["開心","一天"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,9,5,4,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hoi1","sam1","ho2","ji5","gwo3","jat1","tin1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"開心","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"可以","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一天","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"「開心可以過一天」表達了對當下快樂的滿足，儘管這種快樂是短暫的。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0005","text":"但對幾十年 有沒有更寬厚的肩","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["時間","承諾","依賴"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["幾十年","寬厚","肩"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,9,2,0,5,2,5,3,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","deoi3","gei2","sap6","nin4","jau5","mut6","jau5","fun1","hau5","dik1","gin1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"對","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"幾十年","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"有沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"更","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"寬厚","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"肩","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「但對幾十年」將時間尺度拉長，與前一句的「一天」形成對比，並提出對「寬厚肩」的疑問，暗示對長久承諾的渴望與不安。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0006","text":"容顏變 心不變 但眼淺 能見到未來 這是我的底線","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["外貌","情感","未來","底線"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["容顏","心","未來","底線"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,4,3,3,4,2,5,9,0,4,4,2,0,5,2,5,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jung4","ngaan4","bin3","sam1","bat1","bin3","daan6","ngaan5","cin2","nang4","gin3","dou3","mei6","loi4","ze5","si6","ngo5","dik1","dai2","sin3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"容顏","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"變","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"心不變","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"眼淺","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"見到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"未來","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"底線","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「容顏變 心不變」是經典對比，強調內在情感的恆常。「眼淺 能見到未來」是詩意的表達，意指即使目光短淺，也能看到未來，並將此視為自己的「底線」，展現對愛情的堅守。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0007","text":"有些愛太天真 無法生活卻想接吻","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","理想化","現實"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["天真","無法生活","接吻"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,4,4,3,3,0,4,3,2,4,9,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","se1","oi3","taai3","tin1","zan1","mou4","faat3","sang1","wut6","koek3","soeng2","zip3","man5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有些","pos":"DET"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"太天真","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"無法","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"生活","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"卻","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"接吻","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「有些愛太天真」直接批評愛情的不切實際，「無法生活卻想接吻」形成強烈對比，揭示了愛情與現實生活的脫節。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0008","text":"奉獻得天真 救了我感情癮","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["奉獻","依賴","情感癮"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["奉獻","天真","感情癮"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,3,3,3,4,5,5,9,0,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["fung6","hin3","dak1","tin1","zan1","gau3","liu5","ngo5","gam2","cing4","jan2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"奉獻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得","pos":"PART"},{"text":"天真","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"救","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"感情","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"癮","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「奉獻得天真」延續上一句的「天真」，並將其與「奉獻」結合，暗示了無謂的付出。「救了我感情癮」則將這種奉獻視為一種病態的依賴，帶有自嘲和無奈。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0009","text":"無謂再追問 問我的良心","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["追問","良心","自我反省"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["追問","良心"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,3,2,2,5,3,0,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mou4","wai6","zoi3","zeoi1","man6","man6","ngo5","dik1","loeng4","sam1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"無謂","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"追問","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"問","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"良心","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「無謂再追問」表達了對無意義追問的放棄。「問我的良心」則將問題轉向內心，暗示對自己行為的反思。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0010","text":"天色灰暗 全怪我 戀愛路認錯人 / 叨光也太興奮","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["失落","錯誤","興奮"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["天色灰暗","認錯人","興奮"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,4,0,4,5,9,4,2,2,4,0,3,3,5,4,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","sik1","fui1","am3","cyun4","gwaai3","ngo5","lyun2","oi3","lou6","jing6","co3","jan4","dou1","gwong1","jaa5","taai3","hing1","fan5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天色","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"灰暗","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"全怪","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"戀愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"路","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"認錯","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"/","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"叨光","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"PART"},{"text":"太","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"興奮","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「天色灰暗 全怪我 戀愛路認錯人」描繪了失戀後的沮喪和自我歸咎。「叨光也太興奮」則以反諷手法，表達了即使是微小的光芒也讓人過度興奮，突顯了絕望中的一點點希望或麻木。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0011","text":"有些痛叫開心 何妨直認 (怎麼答允) 我這樣笨","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["痛苦","開心","承認","愚笨"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["痛","開心","直認","笨"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,4,4,3,3,0,0,2,2,3,4,5,5,2,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","se1","tung3","giu3","hoi1","sam1","ho4","fong4","zik6","jing6","mo1","daap3","ngo5","ze5","joeng6","ban6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有些","pos":"DET"},{"text":"痛叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"開心","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"何妨","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"直認","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"怎麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"答允","pos":"VERB"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這樣","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"笨","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「有些痛叫開心」是矛盾的表達，將痛苦扭曲為快樂。「何妨直認」表示願意承認。「(怎麼答允) 我這樣笨」則在括號內補充了內心的疑問和對自己愚笨的自嘲。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0012","text":"被擄劫的心 偏差的終點糟蹋太多人 / 糟蹋我都能","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":21},"semantics":{"themes":["被困","傷害","浪費"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["擄劫","心","糟蹋","太多人"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,4,3,3,3,3,3,3,9,3,2,4,3,0,3,2,5,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bei6","lou5","gip3","dik1","sam1","pin1","caa1","dik1","zung1","dim2","zou1","daap6","taai3","do1","jan4","zou1","daap6","ngo5","dou1","nang4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"被","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"擄","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"劫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"偏差","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"終點","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"糟蹋","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"太多人","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"/","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"糟蹋","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"}],"syntax_notes":"「被擄劫的心」比喻心靈被控制。「偏差的終點糟蹋太多人」描述了錯誤的選擇導致的廣泛傷害。「糟蹋我都能」則將這種傷害聚焦到自身，表達了自我毀滅的傾向。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0013","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0013","text":"可能我們 (我堅持) 全被困","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["困境","堅持"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["可能","被困","堅持"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,0,5,0,3,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho2","nang4","ngo5","mun4","gin1","cyun4","bei6","kwan3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"可能","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"我們","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"堅持","pos":"VERB"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"全","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"被困","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「可能我們」帶有不確定性。「(我堅持)」在括號內插入了個人意志，與「可能」形成對比。「全被困」則總結了無力掙脫的狀態。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0014","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
