{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0029","text":"磨蝕 (下半生) 我終身","structure":{"line_index":29,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["消耗","時間","終身"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["磨蝕","下半生","終身"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,3,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mo4","sik6","bun3","sang1","ngo5","zung1","san1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"磨蝕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"下半生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"終身","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「磨蝕」形容時間的消耗。「(下半生)」具體指明了時間範圍。「我終身」則將這種消耗擴展到一生，表達了對時間被浪費的痛惜。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0028","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0030","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0030","text":"有種愛要犧牲 才配得到對方答允","structure":{"line_index":30,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["犧牲","愛情","得到"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["犧牲","配","答允"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,4,4,3,3,0,4,3,4,4,3,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","zung2","oi3","jiu3","hei1","saang1","coi4","pui3","dak1","dou3","deoi3","fong1","daap3","wan5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有種","pos":"DET"},{"text":"愛要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"犧牲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"才","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"配","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"對方","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"答允","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「有種愛要犧牲」提出了一種觀點，認為愛情需要犧牲。「才配得到對方答允」則將這種犧牲與獲得對方認可聯繫起來，暗示了愛情中的不平等交換。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0029","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0031","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0031","text":"大愛的犧牲 最怕博得憐憫","structure":{"line_index":31,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["犧牲","恐懼","憐憫"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["大愛","犧牲","憐憫"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,3,3,3,4,4,4,3,0,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daai6","oi3","dik1","hei1","saang1","zeoi3","paa3","bok3","dak1","lin4","man5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"大愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"犧牲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"最","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"博得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"憐憫","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「大愛的犧牲」是對犧牲的昇華，但「最怕博得憐憫」則暴露了內心的恐懼，害怕這種犧牲只換來同情而非真正的愛。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0030","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0032","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
