{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0033","text":"天色灰暗 仍振作 不再亂認愛人 / 接受錯愛不幸","structure":{"line_index":33,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["振作","不再","接受"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["天色灰暗","振作","不再","愛人"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,4,0,4,4,3,4,2,2,4,0,4,2,4,4,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","sik1","fui1","am3","jing4","zan3","zok3","bat1","zoi3","lyun6","jing6","oi3","jan4","zip3","sau6","co3","oi3","bat1","hang6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天色","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"灰暗","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"仍","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"振作","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"亂認","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"/","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"接受","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"錯愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不幸","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「天色灰暗 仍振作」表達了在困境中仍努力振作的態度。「不再亂認愛人」是決心。「接受錯愛不幸」則是對過去的釋然和對現實的接納。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0032","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0034","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0034","text":"有種愛叫抽身 原來自虐 (分清腳印) 也算罪行","structure":{"line_index":34,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["抽身","自虐","罪行"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["抽身","自虐","罪行"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,4,4,3,3,0,0,2,2,3,4,5,4,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau5","zung2","oi3","giu3","cau1","san1","jyun4","loi4","zi6","joek6","cing1","goek3","jaa5","syun3","zeoi6","hang4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"有種","pos":"DET"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"抽身","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"原來","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"自虐","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"分清","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"腳印","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"也","pos":"PART"},{"text":"算","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"罪行","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「有種愛叫抽身」提出了一種新的愛情觀。「原來自虐」揭示了抽身的本質是自我傷害。「(分清腳印)」是插入的思考。「也算罪行」則將這種自虐行為定性為一種錯誤。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0033","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0035","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
