{"id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0036","text":"同樣要 下決心 誰人沒傷痕","structure":{"line_index":36,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["決心","堅強","傷痕"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["下決心","誰人","傷痕"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,2,4,3,0,0,2,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tung4","joeng6","jiu3","haa6","kyut3","sam1","seoi4","jan4","mut6","soeng1","han4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"同樣","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"下決心","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"沒","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"傷痕","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「同樣要下決心」表達了面對困境的決心。「誰人沒傷痕」則是一種反問，暗示了每個人都有經歷過痛苦，這是一種普遍的狀態，也為接下來的接受鋪墊。"},"source":{"title":"原來只因深愛着","artists":["JW"],"lyricists":["吳業坤","林若寧","陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6283","prev_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0035","next_line_id":"lyr_Slc_NjI4Mw_0037","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
